featured_reviews.review_id:
I used to pray here Jum'aa prayer during my stay there from 1978-80 after crossing a small canal. That time no proper Masjid, no bridge to cross the canal.
Bagdogra is a nice place to get pineapple 50 paise per piece. Three Bengali movies saw in Milani theatre. Cheap local bus fare to go Siliguri- 50 paise. Local people seems to be lovely.

featured_reviews.review_id: Good place to offer daily prayers. The place is located at the center of a slum area and needs support/charity to improve it's infrastructure. The place can accommodate maximum of 30 people at a time. Accessing this place is an issue because of it's complex location and poor roads.
